### Get all sources for the test run
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/sources

### Get specific source details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/sources/facilities-db

### Start the source (if not auto-started)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/sources/facilities-db/start

### Stop the source
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/sources/facilities-db/stop

### Pause the source
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/sources/facilities-db/pause

### Resume the source
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test_runs/test_run_001/sources/facilities-db/resume